wiki.content: “Chulo pt. 2" is a song by Spanish singer Bad Gyal in collaboration with Dominican rapper Tokischa and Puerto Rican Young Miko released on June 22, 2023. The song serves as a continuation of the original song released earlier in the same year. Bad Gyal has said: “I really like the naturalness with which this project came about. “Chulo pt.2” is a very organic collaboration between all of us. Both Tokischa and Young Miko have been able to give another approach to the song, transforming it into a perfect continuation of the original and moving it away from a typical remix.” In addition, Young miko has said: “It's the first song I've done a remix on, and if I'm honest I'm not into remixes. With 'Chulo' it was a necessity, I loved it too much and I felt like I had to be there if that remix was given. In Las Vegas I was more with Bad Gyal and that day she showed me the new version with Tokischa. I wanted to, but I wasn't going to tell him anything. It was she who came forward. I was very excited and that same night I wrote my verse” Read more on Last.fm. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply.
